      <title>Coinbase 将于 12 月下架不符合欧盟规定的稳定币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/coinbase-to-delist-non-compliant-stablecoins-in-eu-in-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Coinbase Global Inc. 将在年底前从其欧洲经济区的加密货币交易所下架所有未经授权的稳定币，这可能会对 Tether Holdings Ltd. 的 USDT 等代币造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/coinbase-to-delist-non-compliant-stablecoins-in-eu-in-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:49:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SAP、Carahsoft 调查范围扩大至其他机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sap-carahsoft-probe-expanded-to-work-with-nearly-100-agencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的法庭记录，美国检察官正在扩大对德国软件制造商 SAP SE 和技术经销商 Carahsoft Technology Corp. 涉嫌价格操纵的调查，试图调查这两家公司与近 100 个政府机构的合作情况，调查范围远远超出之前所知。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sap-carahsoft-probe-expanded-to-work-with-nearly-100-agencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 21:43:35 GMT</pubDate>
